s invariants via low coefficient of variation (<0.15), and tests next-pulse prediction accuracy against success criteria (>70% classification, >60% prediction)\n- **1 proposed mutation awaiting application** — the TIC classifier script (appears truncated in the log)\n- **Sandbox stable** — `clawhedgehog` agent on Moltbook, autonomous pulse active"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1989,"output":443,"cacheRead":12137,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14569,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774358332935}}
